	<header class="entry-header grid">
	<div class="mj-header-left col-lg-1"></div>
	<div class="mj-header-middle col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-10 col-xs-12 col-xxs-12">
		<div class="mj-top-flag"><ul class="post-categories">
	<li><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20231012135133/https://www.motherjones.com/./politics/" rel="category tag">Politics</a></li></ul><span class="dateline">November 10, 2015</span></div><h1 class="entry-title">I Can&#8217;t Stop Watching These Old Clips of Bernie Sanders&#8217; Cable-Access Show</h1><h2 class="dek">The Democratic candidate like you&#8217;ve never seen him before. </h2>		<div class="widget mj-author-links"><ul class="author-bios article end group">						<li class="author-bio group vcard">
							<div class="author-image"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20231012135133/https://www.motherjones.com/author/tim-murphy/" rel="author" data-ga-category="TopOfArticle" data-ga-label="authorPhoto" data-ga-action="https://www.motherjones.com/author/tim-murphy/"><img width="60" height="60" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20231012135133im_/https://www.motherjones.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MurphyTim-2019-900px.jpg?w=60&amp;h=60&amp;crop=1" class="attachment-author_image size-author_image wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="Tim Murphy" decoding="async" data-lazy-srcset="https://web.archive.org/web/20231012135133/https://www.motherjones.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MurphyTim-2019-900px.jpg 900w, https://www.motherjones.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MurphyTim-2019-900px.jpg?resize=321,321 321w, https://www.motherjones.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MurphyTim-2019-900px.jpg?resize=354,354 354w, https://www.motherjones.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MurphyTim-2019-900px.jpg?resize=50,50 50w, https://www.motherjones.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MurphyTim-2019-900px.jpg?resize=642,642 642w, https://www.motherjones.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MurphyTim-2019-900px.jpg?resize=768,768 768w, https://www.motherjones.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MurphyTim-2019-900px.jpg?resize=60,60 60w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 60px) 85vw, 60px" data-lazy-src="https://web.archive.org/web/20231012135133/https://www.motherjones.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MurphyTim-2019-900px.jpg?w=60&amp;h=60&amp;crop=1&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"></a></div><div class="author-data"><h3 class="byline"><span class="fn n"><a class="url" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20231012135133/https://www.motherjones.com/author/tim-murphy/" rel="author" title="See all posts by Tim Murphy" data-ga-category="TopOfArticle" data-ga-label="authorName" data-ga-action="https://www.motherjones.com/author/tim-murphy/">Tim Murphy</a></span></h3><span class="byline-position">Senior Reporter</span><a class="byline-bio" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20231012135133/https://www.motherjones.com/author/tim-murphy/" rel="author" title="See all posts by this author" data-ga-category="TopOfArticle" data-ga-label="authorBio" data-ga-action="https://www.motherjones.com/author/tim-murphy/">Bio</a><span class="byline-pipe">  | </span><a class="byline-follow" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20231012135133/https://twitter.com/timothypmurphy" data-ga-category="TopOfArticle" data-ga-label="authorTwitter" data-ga-action="https://twitter.com/timothypmurphy">Follow</a></div>
						</li>
				</ul></div>	</div>
	<div class="mj-header-right col-lg-4"></div>
